-- W&T Offshore Must Pay $1 Million After Guilty Plea
-- B y   A l l e n   J o h n s o n   J r .
-- 2013-01-04T00:40:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-01-04/w-t-offshore-must-pay-1-million-after-guilty-plea.html
W&T Offshore Inc. (WTI)  was ordered to pay
$1 million in penalties after pleading guilty in federal court
in New Orleans to violating pollution laws, the U.S. said in a
statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Michael Hytha at 
 mhytha@bloomberg.net  